Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:25.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:27.92,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,和大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,逃离这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:32.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是要我们把你抛下吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你一个人不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这样下去你的戒指会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哪怕我会…粉身碎骨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:43.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也要…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:49.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:52.67,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:54.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你就是…
Comment: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:31.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,向塔露拉 同时射击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:34.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,掩护阿米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.07,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她们怎么突然停止行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是战术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,现在可不是磨磨蹭蹭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:02.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,全员 按照指示快速撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,指挥就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:08.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,倒塌的 建筑物废墟中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:12.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有一处空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,从那里穿过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,只要离开广场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在出口的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就有藏身的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们应该…怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.90,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}停下！别四处乱跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,只能死在这里了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:52.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想死…我不想死…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:51.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.44,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}请不要…从我身边离开！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:03:59.90,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:03.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这范围已经…就是极限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,塔露拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.50,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我的手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,居然对同伴见死不救…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:22.64,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:23.67,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,高峰已经过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在第二波到来之前快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,临光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:29.85,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:30.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,了解！
